{
  "stem": "26576.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And those trade union movements, sort accommodated them, did things for them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember meetings.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember even going with my father to certain meetings.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Also, I remember going to Bund meetings.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But those are all vague memories.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't remember so very much about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was-- no, I didn't attend a Bund youth group for a lot of-- I was too young.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By the time, like, you had to be older, 15, 16.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I didn't come to that stage.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was no Yiddish school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This I remember my father always being very upset about it, that from-- no matter how many Jews Sosnowiec had-- there was a Hebrew gymnasium, but there were no Jewish schools.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, when I say Jewish schools, I mean Yiddish-speaking schools.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because he was an Yiddishist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Yiddish was to him very important.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there were no Yiddish-speaking schools.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He always was hoping that one day I would be able to do it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But unfortunately, the war broke it up all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, we were very close to the border.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were very-- how can I say-- we were very much aware.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember when something that I couldn't, at that stage, understand when-- when the Germans sent out Jews like from [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was something.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And a lot of Jews-- several thousands of Jews arrived in Sosnowiec.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we gave even accommodation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were German-speaking Jews, which for us it was a novelty.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, so those were-- that was the beginning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then we heard rage.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were very-- we would listen to Hitler and what Hitler said.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my father kept on constantly-- as long as I remember-- he kept on saying that if the Germans will come here, we will have to run away.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
